                <p>Seoul's Gimpo International Airport is rarely considered by travellers intending to travel to or from South Korea. Indeed, it is true to find an asset among these particular travellers. If Incheon will get much of the attention, this particular, very well-defined, and highly efficient travel experience is mainly for domestic and regional flights, primarily to destinations such as Japan or China.</p>
